  </title>

  <indexterm significance="normal"><primary>Preferences (command)</primary></indexterm>

  
  

  

  

  

  

  

  
  <para>
    The <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">File Preferences</guimenuitem> command displays the
    <link linkend="gimp-prefs-dialog">Preferences dialog</link>,
    which lets you alter a variety of settings that affect the look, feel,
    and performance of the <acronym>GIMP</acronym>.
  </para>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  


